Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:03.47,song,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I check myself cuz I should be dead
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:03.47,song,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我审视自己 因为我本该是死神虎视眈眈的人
